**When TreeMap over HashMap:**
• Need sorted iteration
• Need range queries (subMap, headMap, tailMap)
• Need floor/ceiling (nearest key)

**When HashMap over TreeMap:**
• Only need get/put by exact key (O(1) vs O(log n))
• No ordering requirement

